d former boxer <PERSON> Rubin </PERSON> `` Hurricane'' <PERSON> Carter </PERSON>, who was jailed on triple murder charges, citing racial bias in <PERSON> Carter </PERSON>'s conviction. <PERSON> Sarokin </PERSON> is known for outspoken opinions and ruled mid-way through the cigarette case that the jury had enough evidence to find a tobacco industry conspiracy `` vast in its scope, devious in its purpose and devastating in its results.''
