<HEAD>Meese Rules That IRA Member Should be Deported to UK, Not Ireland</HEAD>
<NOTE>EDs: INSERTS 3 grafs after 8th graf pvs bgng, `Failure to,' to
UPDATE with call for Meese's resignation due to Doherty decision</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By PETE YOST</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
